34:57.804 --> 34:59.931
(train beeps)

35:03.184 --> 35:05.311
(indistinct chatter)

35:07.939 --> 35:09.774
(speaking French)

35:13.569 --> 35:14.987
Le menu.

35:16.114 --> 35:17.865
(phone dings)

35:21.536 --> 35:22.829
(sighs)

35:24.247 --> 35:25.748
(Severine speaking French)

35:30.920 --> 35:33.923
(Karina responding
through phone)

35:36.551 --> 35:39.303
(speaking French)

37:24.283 --> 37:25.743
Edmond: Uh...

37:28.621 --> 37:31.123
(speaking French)

39:13.726 --> 39:15.061
Mmm.

39:15.144 --> 39:17.271
(speaking French)

39:24.487 --> 39:27.865
Mira:
Oh, wow.
That is a lot of bags.

39:27.948 --> 39:29.700
How are we with
hair and make-up?

39:29.784 --> 39:33.454
Uh, we're still
working on the make-up.

39:33.537 --> 39:37.541
You texted.
I was in the neighborhood,
so... here I am.

39:37.625 --> 39:40.419
Yeah, sorry, um, they
now changed the schedule,

39:40.503 --> 39:42.963
-so we don't have much time.
-Doesn't matter.

39:43.047 --> 39:45.299
You know, I thought
I missed film shoots,

39:45.382 --> 39:47.134
I really did,
but... turns out

39:47.218 --> 39:49.220
I don't miss 'em at all.
(chuckles)

39:54.892 --> 39:57.019
You're wearing
the costume.

39:57.103 --> 39:59.939
Yeah, they, uh,
need me in the catsuit.

40:01.148 --> 40:03.692
-Show me.
-No.

40:03.776 --> 40:05.569
Come on... please.

40:05.653 --> 40:06.904
No.

40:07.696 --> 40:08.864
Show me how hot you are.

40:08.948 --> 40:11.492
You know how hot I am.
Quite well.

40:12.451 --> 40:14.453
-I forget.
-Oh, you do.

40:14.537 --> 40:16.705
Mm-hm.
Take off your coat.

40:22.711 --> 40:23.796
Good girl.

40:24.713 --> 40:26.340
-Happy?
-Mm-hm.

40:27.716 --> 40:29.426
Why don't you stand up?

40:29.510 --> 40:33.431
-(Mira chuckles)
-Come on. Stand up, Mira.

40:36.600 --> 40:37.852
(clears throat)

40:37.935 --> 40:41.063
And now, do it like you
used to do it for me.

40:41.147 --> 40:43.399
(chuckles)
Do it.

40:46.735 --> 40:47.903
Laurie: Mm.

40:49.697 --> 40:51.532
Wow.

40:51.615 --> 40:53.742
-Yeah.
-It's very cool.

40:56.412 --> 40:57.746
Now turn around.

40:59.582 --> 41:00.875
Turn around.

41:11.010 --> 41:12.511
Ta-da!

41:15.055 --> 41:16.891
They're looking at me.

41:16.974 --> 41:19.143
I like when they look at you.

41:19.226 --> 41:20.519
It's embarrassing.

41:20.603 --> 41:22.271
But you're turned on.

41:24.273 --> 41:26.650
I don't want the crew
to see me like this.

41:26.734 --> 41:29.612
I know you when
you're turned on.

41:30.696 --> 41:32.198
I don't know.

41:34.658 --> 41:36.702
You can sit. I'm happy.

41:44.418 --> 41:46.337
You know what I did today?

41:46.420 --> 41:47.713
Mm.

41:47.796 --> 41:49.215
Yeah, I don't know.
Um, let me guess.

41:49.298 --> 41:50.925
I think the reason why you...

41:51.008 --> 41:53.385
put all these bags on display

41:53.469 --> 41:56.639
might be because you've
been on a couture spree.

41:56.722 --> 41:58.307
-Correct.
-Mm.

41:58.390 --> 42:01.143
All the stores that
you used to take me to.

42:01.227 --> 42:02.436
Back when I was
doing the buying,

42:02.519 --> 42:05.105
-and you were
schlepping the bags.
-Mm-hm.

42:06.273 --> 42:08.234
-Yes.
-And now you have your revenge.

42:08.317 --> 42:10.986
Oh, no.
No, no, no.
(chuckles)

42:11.070 --> 42:13.989
My revenge is to feel like
I have you wrapped
around my little finger.

42:14.073 --> 42:15.824
-You do.
-I know.

42:17.451 --> 42:18.786
Sit back.

42:24.333 --> 42:26.460
Put your hands on the armchair.

42:30.297 --> 42:32.049
Now open your legs.

42:34.301 --> 42:35.636
Not too much.

42:37.179 --> 42:38.138
There.

42:39.223 --> 42:40.349
Like this?

42:43.435 --> 42:45.187
Are you satisfied?

42:45.688 --> 42:46.814
Yes.

42:48.565 --> 42:50.526
I like that very much.

42:52.653 --> 42:54.113
Do you want me back?

42:57.574 --> 42:59.201
Say it.

42:59.285 --> 43:03.122
I want you back... please.

43:04.540 --> 43:05.874
Say it again.

43:08.752 --> 43:11.171
Please, Laurie, I want you back.

43:11.255 --> 43:13.799
God, you're sexy when you beg.

43:14.508 --> 43:15.801
(chuckles)

43:16.844 --> 43:19.471
But I have to go.

43:19.555 --> 43:22.391
I have to drop off
all of these bags
at the Plaza Athénée.

43:22.474 --> 43:25.185
I'm moving out of there.

43:25.269 --> 43:29.148
-Where to?
-Some cheaper place
the French production booked.

43:29.231 --> 43:31.400
Hm. You know what, darling?

43:32.693 --> 43:34.987
I'm glad I skipped this one.

43:35.070 --> 43:37.197
Will I see you before you leave?

43:42.411 --> 43:44.455
If you come
to the Plaza Athénée...

43:46.707 --> 43:50.794
maybe we can have a drink...

43:50.878 --> 43:51.795
or two.

43:53.422 --> 43:54.965
What would you
say to that?

43:56.967 --> 43:59.094
Mm, 6:30-ish.

44:01.764 --> 44:03.307
I know you'll be there.

44:04.808 --> 44:07.936
(classical music playing)

44:21.283 --> 44:22.618
(speaking French)

44:29.124 --> 44:31.293
(music plays from video)

44:41.470 --> 44:43.931
(speaking French)

45:26.890 --> 45:27.891
Okay. Okay.

45:27.975 --> 45:31.687
(speaking French)

46:18.734 --> 46:19.693
Okay.

46:19.776 --> 46:21.653
(speaking French)

46:21.737 --> 46:24.907
(tense music playing)

46:26.825 --> 46:29.453
(classical piano plays)

46:37.127 --> 46:38.795
Philippe:
I'll take my leave.

46:39.963 --> 46:41.089
I love you.

46:41.965 --> 46:43.050
Break a leg.

46:47.387 --> 46:49.598
-Good evening.
-(thunder rumbles)

46:53.519 --> 46:55.604
♪ ♪

47:00.943 --> 47:03.695
Dear artist, allow me
to introduce myself:

47:03.779 --> 47:06.114
I am the Count of Noirmoutier.

47:06.198 --> 47:08.492
A modest admirer.

47:10.369 --> 47:14.915
My Lord, I'm greatly honored
by your interest in my work.

47:14.998 --> 47:17.209
Would you accord me
the infinite pleasure

47:17.292 --> 47:20.462
of joining me
for supper tonight

47:20.546 --> 47:23.090
after your performance?

47:23.173 --> 47:27.594
-I do not know whether I should.
-Yes, I understand.

47:27.678 --> 47:32.391
Accept this gift as proof
of my noble intentions.

47:33.016 --> 47:35.102
♪ ♪

47:39.398 --> 47:40.983
(chuckles)

47:41.066 --> 47:43.443
That is such
a generous present.

47:43.527 --> 47:47.239
It is but a small token
of my profound admiration.

47:47.322 --> 47:50.117
Let me help
you put it on.

47:51.285 --> 47:52.202
Please.

47:58.750 --> 48:00.252
(speaking French)

48:12.180 --> 48:13.557
(yells)

48:13.640 --> 48:15.183
(speaking French)

49:41.770 --> 49:44.773
-Bellman: Please.
-One, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight.

49:44.856 --> 49:47.484
-All good. Thank you.
-You're welcome.

49:47.567 --> 49:50.195
Two minutes, please.
I'll be right back.

49:53.448 --> 49:56.034
Okay. Car's loaded
and ready to go.

49:56.118 --> 49:58.328
I'll join you later.
I told you I have a meeting.

49:58.412 --> 50:01.957
It's 7.
I thought your meeting
was at 6:30?

50:02.040 --> 50:04.501
Yeah, obviously,
they're running late.

50:04.584 --> 50:06.712
What about your new suite?
You don't wanna check it out?

50:06.795 --> 50:10.215
-I trust you.
-That's unlike you.

50:11.883 --> 50:13.927
I'll be there
in half an hour.
Take the van.

50:14.010 --> 50:15.303
I'll keep the chauffeur.

50:15.387 --> 50:16.430
Okay.

50:16.513 --> 50:18.640
(indistinct chatter)

50:21.184 --> 50:24.354
(speaking French)

50:27.733 --> 50:30.026
(speaking French)

51:59.366 --> 52:00.951
(laughs)

52:01.034 --> 52:03.078
(speaking French)

53:02.637 --> 53:05.765
(lounge music playing)

53:17.861 --> 53:18.945
Hi.

53:24.117 --> 53:26.661
-Wow.
-Oh, thank you.

53:26.745 --> 53:28.997
Now I understand why
it took some time.

53:29.080 --> 53:31.374
Well, I did
say 6:30-ish.

53:31.458 --> 53:33.919
Well, the "-ish" ended
about 40 minutes ago.

53:34.002 --> 53:35.962
I had dresses that
needed alterations,

53:36.046 --> 53:37.714
and they just kept me
waiting and waiting,

53:37.797 --> 53:39.841
but...
I'm used to that.

53:39.925 --> 53:41.468
I often waited
for your dresses.

53:41.551 --> 53:43.678
-True.
-Waiter: Would you
like to order, Madam?

53:43.762 --> 53:46.806
Um, no, actually,
I'm, I'm fine.

53:46.890 --> 53:50.560
I... I should be
going actually.

53:52.562 --> 53:55.732
Are you fucking
kidding me?

53:55.815 --> 53:57.484
I have dinner
with Herman.

53:57.567 --> 54:00.946
It's our last night in Paris.
We go back to LA tomorrow.

54:01.029 --> 54:05.075
He booked this amazing
reservation somewhere,
but he won't tell me where.

54:05.158 --> 54:08.203
He wants it
to be a surprise.
How cute is that?

54:08.286 --> 54:11.706
-Yeah, how kind of him.
-He's a kind man.

54:11.790 --> 54:14.626
Well... I have to go,

54:14.709 --> 54:18.713
but we'll have
more time in LA.

54:18.797 --> 54:24.094
-Will we?
-Yeah, I think we're in a more
balanced relationship now,

54:24.177 --> 54:26.680
so we could spend
more time together.

54:26.763 --> 54:28.056
Fuck you, Laurie.

54:28.139 --> 54:29.432
Not yet.

